    "description": "<h3><strong>Hearth Global</strong></h3><p>At Hearth Global, we believe legacy isn't built alone—it's built with a family behind you.</p><p>We are a global sales and strategic facilitation partner for families of significance, family offices, and next-generation leaders. Our primary business is managing tailored sales campaigns and fostering trusted connections for a diverse international client portfolio. But our purpose runs deeper.</p><p>We specialize in welcoming newcomers into a worldwide kinship. We don't just execute campaigns; we initiate, integrate, and guide. Our work connects each member to a curated ecosystem of elite resources, advisors, and peer communities, transforming complex challenges into opportunities for harmony, growth, and generational stewardship.</p><p>Think of us as the guardians of the gateway. Whether navigating wealth transition, governance, education, or strategic investments, we provide the relational framework and expert facilitation that turns outsiders into insiders, and individual clients into a global family.</p>",
